refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     1.3.3

      返回的值修改为兼容
      MongoClient::setReadPreference。
      type 的值从数组改成字符串，删除了
      type_string，并且
      tagsets 现在以键值表示的标签而不是冒号分隔的字符串。

  &reftitle.examples;

   MongoClient::getReadPreference 返回值例子


<?php

$m = new MongoClient();
$m->setReadPreference(MongoClient::RP_SECONDARY, array(
    array('dc' => 'east', 'use' => 'reporting'),
    array('dc' => 'west'),
    array(),
));
var_dump($m->getReadPreference());
?>


   &example.outputs;


array(2) {
  ["type"]=>
  string(9) "secondary"
  ["tagsets"]=>
  array(3) {
    [0]=>
    array(2) {
      ["dc"]=>
      string(4) "east"
      ["use"]=>
      string(9) "reporting"
    }
    [1]=>
    array(1) {
      ["dc"]=>
      string(7) "west"
    }
    [2]=>
    array(0) {
    }
  }
}

